DIGEST
SB 170 Original 2026 Regular Session Pressly
Present law creates the Caddo-Bossier Parishes Port Commission and establishes
requirements for commissioners.
Proposed law adds the requirement that commissioners be appointed subject to Senate
confirmation.
Proposed law further requires commissioners to have expertise in economic development,
transportation, logistics, or commercial real estate.
Proposed law provides for technical changes.
Effective August 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 34:3158)
